org.bytemechanics.commons.collections

Class DropLastQueue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytemechanics.commons.collections.DropLastQueue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - 

    public class DropLastQueue<T>
extends Object
    Synchronized queue that keeps the same size whatever adds done by droping the extra elements from the head This implementation is not fast but never overflow the initial size
    Author:
    afarre
